TITLE: National Assembly election report presented to President Paudel
BODY:
The report on the National Assembly election held on January 25 has been submitted to President Ramchandra Paudel. Officiating Chief Election Commissioner Ram Prasad Bhandari presented the report to the President at a ceremony held at the Rastrapati Bhawan, Shital Niwas, today.
